title: History of Toyota
author: Unknown
pages:
Once a small division
of a loom company, the
Toyota Corportation
has risen to become a
preeminant auto giant
that could buy
Detroit's big 3 with its
pocket change. The
compact Corolla is an
omnipresent nameplate
that can be found
across the planet,
and subsaharan
Africa would be

difficult to picture
without being dotted
with dusty Hiluxes -
sometimes with machine
guns.
